section.section:
Grounds for disqualification of a hearing officer shall include, but shall not be limited to, the following:
Serving as an investigator or prosecutor in the proceeding or the preadjudicative stages of the proceeding;
Participating in an ex parte communication which would prejudice the proceedings;
Having a pecuniary interest in the outcome of the proceeding; or
Having a personal bias toward any party to a proceeding which would cause a prejudgment on the outcome of the proceeding.
